title: Cilla Black - Best Of Cilla Black
description:
Songs from pop vocalist Cilla Black's early career shine in this 25-track anthology.

2002 reissue of 1968 compilation includes 11 bonus tracks (some of which have never previously been available on CD), 'Surround Yourself With Sorrow', ...
